      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained interior, reflects a standard of care that exceeds the highest expectations. The mechanical integrity is absolute, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality for the discerning collector.",
