      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
