    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. This meticulously maintained masterpiece features a flawless exterior with its original, deep-gloss paint and zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state\u2014completely smoke-free, with the premium leather upholstery still firm and free of any wear or creasing. Every electronic component and convenience feature operates exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history and a pristine engine bay with absolutely no leaks or aging. Garage-kept and driven only in fair weather, this is the definitive example for a discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
